```class Solution {
    public int minimizedStringLength(String s) {
        int res = s.length();
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            char c = s.charAt(i);
            int left = i, right = i;
            while (left >= 0 && s.charAt(left) == c) left--;
            while (right < s.length() && s.charAt(right) == c) right++;
            res = Math.min(res, s.length() - (right - left - 1));
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
